FBIS4-50251 "drchi095_b_94004" FBIS-CHI-94-095 Daily Report 17 May 1994 United States & Canada Defense Minister Chi Haotian Meets U.S. Guests Defense Minister Chi Haotian Meets U.S. Guests OW1705091794 Beijing XINHUA in English 0859 GMT 17 May 94 OW1705091794 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 17 (XINHUA) -- Chinese State Councillor and National Defense Minister Chi Haotian met here this morning with Zbigniew Brzezinski, former U.S. national security adviser, and Michael Oksenberg, president of the East-West Center of the United States. The U.S. guests came at the invitation of the Chinese People's Institute of Foreign Affairs.
